  "text": "Considered as an endocrine organ, the skin can be also seen as a mirror for many tumoral and nontumoral diseases. Many skin conditions appear to be the result of hormonal disfunctions, both hormone excess and hormone deficiency/resistance, as well as growth factor pathological signaling [CITATION_1] .",
